      "timestampEdited": null,
      "callEndedTimestamp": null,
      "isPinned": false,
      "content": "I would think that waiting after run #1 is done and people had time to test is a good idea.  Unless there is is enough demand to completely fill a run #2 before that ( which I doubt ), I don't really see any benefit into making it before.",
